                 mdef=map.def
                 name=archsites
                 pen=1
                 size=.2
                 rot=0
                 just=l
                 font=sr
                 x=.2
                 y=0
            
            NOTE            NOTE
            If the MAPGEN sites file specified does not exist, the
            command assumes the user wants to use a GRASS file.
            
            The delete key will abort the make.label command.                                          __________         
            
